Isolation levels (tradeoffs between consistency and concurrency):
- READ UNCOMMITTED: see dirty reads
- READ COMMITTED: no dirty reads (PostgreSQL default)
- REPEATABLE READ: no phantom reads (MySQL default)
- SERIALIZABLE: fully isolated (slowest)

